        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 080efb03-a66a-401e-b6df-4eac496e9e2d).Image",
        "Description": "Sorry to interupt your journey 47, but a development has occured. Alexa uncovered that it was Emma and Gregory whomst killed Nathanial, and has contacted us to take them out. Of course, Alexa has no idea she&apos;s also on the list. Three birds, one stone.\r\rAlexa requested her children&apos;s deaths look like accidents so as to not arrouse more suspicion, and I would suggest the same for Alexa to stay consistent. She also requested no deaths befall her staff. Good luck, 47.",
